subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Leander Paes and Lukas Dlouhy beat the No. 3 seeds, Mahesh Bhupathi and Mark Knowles, 3-6, 6-3, 6-2, in the United States Open doubles final.
